title: Chapter 1233 - What Do You Mean, I Can Live A Little Longer?
volume_title: His Sword Takes Aim A The Three Thousand Worlds Of The Stars, Suppressing Foes Both Past And Present
body:
Chapter 1233 - What Do You Mean, I Can Live A Little Longer?

“They’re finally getting even!” 

Numerous cultivators appeared off in the distance. All were experts of Flying Cloud Tower, the Divine Star Church, the Thousand Demons Cult, and the Black Lotus Sect.

They gazed at the distant dome of heaven, their expressions full of eagerness and excitement.

Beneath the firmament.

Five World Kings appeared, each presiding over a different area. Their auras locked onto Su Yi and Meng Changyun from afar.

Rather, all of them locked onto Meng Changyun.

As for Su Yi? They didn’t attach any importance to him. His aura was reserved to the extreme, almost non-existent.

Combined with his youth, this made him easy to overlook.

Although Meng Changyun was also keeping a low profile, when he appeared, he revealed the characteristic aura of the late-stage Heavenly Longevity Realm.

“Before you hit a dog, you ought to check and see who its master is. Fellow Daoist, you’re a World King, yet you slew our subordinates here in Skyblue City. Don’t you think that’s over the line?” A white-haired elder said expressionlessly.

He held a black alms bowl aloft. His hair and beard fluttered around him, and his majesty was imposing.
